stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> q_start
    q_start --> q_find_star: başla
    q_find_star --> q_find_star: 0/1 oku, R
    q_find_star --> q_return_left: * oku
    q_return_left --> q_return_left: sola dön
    q_return_left --> q_read_multiplicand: sol sınır
    q_read_multiplicand --> q_read_multiplicand: 0/1 oku
    q_read_multiplicand --> q_read_multiplier: * oku
    q_read_multiplier --> q_read_multiplier: 0/1 oku
    q_read_multiplier --> q_init_result: = oku
    q_init_result --> q_seek_multiplier_bit: sonuç = 0
    q_seek_multiplier_bit --> q_read_multiplier_bit: sağdan sola bit seç
    q_read_multiplier_bit --> q_skip_zero: 0 -> x
    q_skip_zero --> q_seek_multiplier_bit: sonraki shift
    q_read_multiplier_bit --> q_copy_multiplicand: 1 -> y
    q_copy_multiplicand --> q_add_partial: parçalı çarpım = multiplicand << shift
    q_add_partial --> q_clear_work: ikili toplama
    q_clear_work --> q_write_result: geçici alan temiz
    q_write_result --> q_seek_multiplier_bit: sonuç güncel
    q_seek_multiplier_bit --> q_restore_multiplier: bit kalmadı
    q_restore_multiplier --> q_restore_multiplier: x->0, y->1
    q_restore_multiplier --> q_accept: = konumu
    q_accept --> [*]
    q_find_star --> q_reject: geçersiz sembol
    q_read_multiplicand --> q_reject: geçersiz sembol
    q_read_multiplier --> q_reject: geçersiz sembol
